      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/trivia/work/259320-lamb-in-his-bosom">Trivia About Lamb in His Bosom</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
